text: Bubenreuth is a municipality in the district of Erlangen-Höchstadt, in Bavaria, Germany. == Place == Bubenreuth is near the river Regnitz and ca. 4 kilometers north of Erlangen with which it's structurally connected. Neighboring towns are (from North clockwise) Baiersdorf, Langensendelbach, Marloffstein, Erlangen and Möhrendorf. == References == Category:Erlangen- Höchstadt
